sub_title: Professional in Government and International Relations
summary:
Professional with ability to work in team and under pressure, charismatic with ethical and moral values, with a high competition in acquiring new skills in organizational and administrative terms and ability to establish successful relationships with public and private actors. 

I have a good command of foreign languages ​​and I am a person with skills to interact with others and build a productive work environment with a discretionary management and reservation of the information. I have a special interest in the learning and development area  as well as Teaching.  In addition to the study of new technologies and data analysis tools like Power BI.
